title: Ep. 226 - The End Is Upon Us
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, the Green New Deal failed in the Senate and we’re all going to die. Also, the prosecutor who dropped charges against Jussie Smollet admits that he’s guilty. And the NYT tries to disprove God. Did they succeed? We’ll discuss. Date: 03-27-2019
